6: This makes how many times now?
11:
That should be more than enough.
We can see she's got what it takes, I
don't see a problem takin' her along.
17:
Nimbus, how could you say
something so irresponsible?
20:
Does it matter? She's gonna tag
along with us whether we approve
or not.
21: Or would you rather we ditch her?
26:
Listen here, Kyrie. While you're with
us, we will be acting as your
parents! Make sure not to do
anything reckless!
31:
Ohmigosh, there are so many
different guns here! I can't believe
there are guns on this world too!
34:
Cooool, this one is super unique…
This one's shape is all funky… and...
37:
This gun... It's a family heirloom that
was stolen from our house years
ago! And this one! And this one too!
42:
Wait a minute, Kyrie. That can't
be—we're in a totally different world
now!
47:
What… no! There's zero chance that
I'm mixing them up. ZERO! I'd
recognize this crest anywhere!
50:
What are you lot going on about
here? I can't have you running your
mouth like that about my precious
wares!
55:
S-sorry, b-but please—have a look
at this! It's identical to mine!
58:
The shape, the crest... The
resemblance is indeed there.
61:
See? That proves it!
You stole this from my family!
64:
Preposterous! These wares were
sold to me by a trusted patron of
mine! How dare you suggest they
were stolen!
71:
It stands to reason that these
firearms were not originally of this
world. I suppose we'll need to learn
more about this trusted patron of
his.
78:
You sure this the right place? I don't
think you need my nose to tell you
that this place reeks something sus.
88:
*sniff* There's no way I'd be all right
in a place like this!
94:
If you're scared, you can feel free to
turn back now.
98:
Okay! I… I… It's no use, I can't do it! Or,
wait, maybe I can…
105: Who the hell are you lot?
107:
Don't think we haven't seen you
skulking around and makin' a ruckus
around here! State yer business!
111:
W-we saw a gun that looked just like
this one... in the town nearby… We
were wondering how you got your
hands on it?
114:
Oh? You seem to be quite informed,
little missus.
116:
Oy, grab 'em all before they get
away!
120:
Eeeeek! D-d-d-don't you come any
closer!
123: Whoa, whoa! Calm down now. Don't—
126: Waugh! I just can't do it! I can't!
131:
I don't think I need to ask, but... are
you okay, Kyrie?
139:
Hmm, the bullet just barely missed
him by a hair, just as before. It's
nothing short of a miracle.
148:
You, um, you'll return my precious
family heirloom now, won't you?
151: Y-yes, whatever you want! Of course!
157:
We'll have someone from the guild
come over to question you even
further, so no funny business. Got it?
159:
Yes, yes, I understand. Just take the
gun and be on your way!
165:
Heh-heh... Now that I've taken a
closer look at it, this isn't actually my
family's heirloom!
173:
It's made of a much lighter material
than I remember... and look! The
workmanship is totally off. This is just
a really well-made replica! Haha!
176:
But isn't it odd? All those guns we
confiscated from that cave looked
exactly the same!
181:
That can only mean that this replica
was mass produced… somewhere
on another world?
184:
We'll need to investigate further!
And I'm the only one who can tell
the difference!
190:
You've fashioned together a new
excuse to stick around, I see. Isn't it
past time for you to return home,
young lady?
195: Aw, don't be such a sourpuss, Light!
